				<font face="verdana" size="2"><blockquote>
<p>
We have wrapped up the most recent poll today with 794 votes giving a good 16% of the people to have spent over 3000$ in computer equipment in the last year. Here are the results from the poll:</p>
<p>
How much computer equipment and periphreals have you purchased in the last 12 months? This includes Computers, Mice, Monitors, Sound/Graphic Cards, Networking equipment etc.</p>
<p>
0-50$ (76 voted) 10 %<br>
51-150$ (52 voted) 7 %<br>
151-300$ (79 voted) 10 %<br>
301-600$ (90 voted) 11 %<br>
601-900$ (80 voted) 10 %<br>
901-1200$ (75 voted) 9 %<br>
1201-1500$ (45 voted) 6 %<br>
1501-2000$ (81 voted) 10 %<br>
2001$-3000$ (86 voted) 11 %<br>
3001$+ (130 voted) 16 %</p>
<p>
Today's poll is about roleplaying in EverQuest. How many people ACTUALLY roleplay? Simply vote on the poll on the right part of the page or via our <a href="http://www.everlore.com/polls/default.asp"  >polls</a> section. Special thanks to Civeaux for the poll suggestion.</p>
<p>
If you would like credit on any Everlore future polls, please drop by our <A href="http://www.everlore.com/MB_TOPICS.asp?fid=183&FN=Poll+Suggestions&sid=7&SN=EverQuest&SURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Eeverlore%2Ecom&Cat=General&PL=2"  >Poll suggestions Forum</a>.</p>
