<blockquote>
<p>
This week's <a href="http://www.planeteverquest.com/features/quiz/index.shtml"  >EQ Quiz is about Frogloks</a>.  They live all around us, deep within some of the most dangerous dungeons of the lands and walk freely in many other zones. They are non-hostile to those of goodly gods and strike fiercly at those who worship the evil ones. How much do you know about these amphibians?</p>
<p>
This "just for fun" quiz will challenge all that you know, or might not know, about Frogloks.  Take the test and see how much you know .. or don't know about the Frog People of EQ.</p>
<p>
