Not as good of a turnout as I had expected, only 8 of the 15 that signed up showed but we decided to hold it anyway...</p>
<p>
We made our way to the FP Arena and found a few lvl 60s and some 55+ waiting there for us as I had expected 8)... </p>
<p>
I asked the guild if they could clear them out and 4 members came to help us out, they said it would take some time so we held the tourny outside FP Gates and hoped when we were done arena would be clear for the battle royal..</p>
<p>
Well Tigarius came out of top in the tournament with Joraz following him in second place</p>
<p>
Blodd of Honor had gave us the go ahead on the tourny destroying n e one that stepped foot in the arena but the particapants...</p>
<p>
Tigarius again came out on top in the Battle Royal</p>
<p>
GOOD JOB TIGARIUS</p>
