				<font face="verdana" size="3"><a name="20">Bertoxx Organized Nagafen Raid 7/20</a></font><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<b><a href="mailto:shadowdragon77@home.com">Vdayan Windrider</b></a>
				[7/16/2001-2:16:30 PM]</font>
				&nbsp;<a href="Comments.asp?ID=468181"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Comments[9]</font></a><p>
				<font face="verdana" size="2"><blockquote>
<p>
Faydwer's Brethren, assisted by Harbingers of Innorruk and Tribal Soldiers will be hosting an ORGANIZED Nagafen Raid on July 20th at 9:00pm Eastern US time.</p>
<p>
This is NOT a pick up raid. <b>RSVP by Email only.</b> <b><u>NO show ups will be allowed to participate</u>.</b> Our objective is to obtain the red dragon scale for Colosis Gladorion.</p>
<p>
The Roster of confirmed participants is already very full, however <b>we are looking for 4 clerics, 2 Enchanters and 4 wizards to fill the remaining spots.</b> Need them to be level 49 plus.</p>
<p>
We invite mentally mature people who can listen and abide fully by our Rules and plan. All Participants should review our raid rules and All strategies BEFORE the raid on our <a href="http://members.home.net/bigdragon7/dragonraid/index.htm"    >Guide To Dragon Raids Website </a></p>
<p>
Please check the Website and read it. <b>If you are interested in attending, EMAIL us from the website and let us know your name, class and level.</b>  Also let us know in that email that you have gone to the website and understand the rules and strategy.</p>
<p>
People who register may wish to become part of a Regular raid group to do future dragon and planes raids.</p>
<p>
Thank you!</p>
<p>
Sincerely,<br>
Vdayan Windrider<br>
Founder of Faydwer's Brethren</p>
